<p>Thank you for your valuable feedback regarding the proposal for <b>{{OPPORTUNITY_NAME}}</b>. We understand that flexibility is key, and we have reworked the payment schedule to better align with your requirements.</p>

<div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 5px solid #6c757d; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;"><strong style="color: #495057;">Based on your request:</strong><br />
