<p style="margin-top: 25px;"><a href="{{APPROVAL_LINK}}" style="background-color: #198754; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 14px;">View &amp; Accept Updated Terms </a></p>

<p>If you have any further questions, please do not hesitate to reach out to your primary contact, <b>{{OWNER_NAME}}</b>.</p>

<hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 20px 0;" />
